00:02:53.160 --> 00:02:58.940
avoided. The human predicament has something, some distinctive features

49
00:02:58.940 --> 00:03:01.679
to it. Uh, FOR example, I think as far

50
00:03:01.679 --> 00:03:04.839
as we know, humans are the only creatures that

