00:03:45.210 --> 00:03:47.690
a quality of life that is much, much lower

64
00:03:47.690 --> 00:03:50.919
than many, many human beings' quality of life. And

65
00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:53.440
so that's a way in which their predicament is

