00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.830
worse than certainly many humans, but perhaps not all

67
00:03:55.830 --> 00:03:56.380
humans.

68
00:03:57.500 --> 00:04:02.070
Would you extend at least some aspects of this

69
00:04:02.630 --> 00:04:06.490
predicament to all sentient life?

70
00:04:07.550 --> 00:04:09.789
Yes, uh, that, uh, that is the case. I,

71
00:04:09.869 --> 00:04:11.800
I think, as you will be aware from some

72
00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:15.029
of my earlier work that I think it's a

73
00:04:15.029 --> 00:04:17.790
harm to any sentient being to be brought into

74
00:04:17.790 --> 00:04:23.109
existence. And, uh, it's also a harm to cause

75
00:04:23.109 --> 00:04:24.910
a sentient being to cease to exist. That is

76
00:04:24.910 --> 00:04:27.230
to say, to kill a sentient being or for

