81
00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:39.100
and individual to individual.

82
00:04:40.640 --> 00:04:45.010
When it comes to this predicament we find ourselves

83
00:04:45.010 --> 00:04:48.649
in as humans, do you think that it is

84
00:04:48.649 --> 00:04:55.570
inevitable that people will get across it, that people

85
00:04:55.570 --> 00:04:59.809
will know at least to some extent that they

86
00:04:59.809 --> 00:05:06.385
are in this predicament. Or should we tell them

87
00:05:06.385 --> 00:05:08.864
and and I mean if do you think that

88
00:05:08.864 --> 00:05:14.144
people should know or should be told that they

89
00:05:14.144 --> 00:05:17.005
are in this predicament if they just so happen

90
00:05:17.005 --> 00:05:20.285
to not be aware of it for some reason?

91
00:05:21.369 --> 00:05:23.649
I certainly think it's possible for people not to

92
00:05:23.649 --> 00:05:25.489
