00:06:28.140 --> 00:06:31.179
people about it, but I also think it matters

113
00:06:31.179 --> 00:06:34.619
how and when you tell them. Uh, I, I

114
00:06:34.619 --> 00:06:37.260
don't think that one should go up to people

115
00:06:37.260 --> 00:06:39.779
