00:06:50.380 --> 00:06:53.779
is among the acceptable ways to convey this message

121
00:06:53.779 --> 00:06:54.320
to people.

122
00:06:55.269 --> 00:06:58.220
But do you think that there are perhaps cases

123
00:06:58.220 --> 00:07:03.940
or situations where it would be more moral for

