00:07:33.989 --> 00:07:36.029
I agree. I think there certainly are. And one

130
00:07:36.029 --> 00:07:37.899
kind of case that comes to mind is somebody's

131
00:07:37.899 --> 00:07:40.500
on their deathbed, and they may be speaking to

