00:08:07.959 --> 00:08:10.000
much harm to anybody else at that point. It's

144
00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:12.390
bringing them some comfort, and I think we should

145
00:08:12.390 --> 00:08:13.820
just leave, leave it alone.

146
00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:19.850
So of course this question or these issues surrounding

147
00:08:20.220 --> 00:08:25.390
how our human predicament ties a lot to the

148
00:08:25.390 --> 00:08:31.149
meaning or lack thereof of our lives. So what

