152
00:08:42.648 --> 00:08:47.900
Uh, I sympathize with those views that See meaning

153
00:08:48.059 --> 00:08:53.770
as having some purpose or point or significance. And

154
00:08:53.770 --> 00:08:57.559
so, typically that would involve having some impact, uh,

155
00:08:57.570 --> 00:08:59.609
pos and presumably a positive impact if what you're

156
00:08:59.609 --> 00:09:01.729
looking for is positive meaning, because there can also

157
00:09:01.729 --> 00:09:05.520
be a negative meaning. To have some positive impact

158
00:09:05.520 --> 00:09:09.020
on, on others that can make a life meaningful,

159
00:09:09.059 --> 00:09:13.250
and I do think that our lives can Generate

