163
00:09:21.650 --> 00:09:23.950
I do think there are different perspectives from which

164
00:09:24.010 --> 00:09:26.650
one's life can have or lack meaning. And I

165
00:09:26.650 --> 00:09:29.969
think it's most likely to, our lives are most

166
00:09:29.969 --> 00:09:33.809
likely to have meaning in very narrow circles. So,

167
00:09:34.130 --> 00:09:38.809
almost everybody. Has some meaning to people adjacent to

168
00:09:38.809 --> 00:09:41.130
them, to their family members, to their friends. They

169
00:09:41.130 --> 00:09:44.289
have some, they, their life has some point with

170
00:09:44.289 --> 00:09:46.710
respect to people in those circles. There's some people

171
00:09:46.929 --> 00:09:49.250
for whom their lives have a broader effect, a

172
00:09:49.250 --> 00:09:52.609
broader meaning. Some people will have an effect on

173
00:09:52.609 --> 00:09:54.929
all of humanity, a positive effect on all of

174
00:09:54.929 --> 00:09:58.440
humanity. One of the examples I gave is Uh,

175
00:09:58.530 --> 00:10:01.340
so Alexander Fleming, who discovers penicillin, and this now

176
00:10:01.340 --> 00:10:05.020
has a very beneficial effect for millions of human

