00:10:05.020 --> 00:10:10.719
beings. Even after he dies. And so those are

178
00:10:10.719 --> 00:10:13.559
ways in which lives can sometimes have very extensive,

179
00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:16.919
what I call terrestrial meanings. But I think that

