00:10:21.799 --> 00:10:24.719
something like a cosmic perspective, no lives in fact

183
00:10:24.719 --> 00:10:26.260
have meaning from that perspective.

184
00:10:27.010 --> 00:10:29.919
OK, tell us a little bit more about that.

185
00:10:30.090 --> 00:10:35.070
Uh, WHAT do you mean exactly by cosmic meaning

186
00:10:35.210 --> 00:10:39.909
and terrestrial meaning? Uh, HOW do you distinguish one

187
00:10:40.169 --> 00:10:40.929
from the other?

188
00:10:42.030 --> 00:10:45.989
Well, terrestrial really refers to earthly meaning. So we

189
00:10:45.989 --> 00:10:48.750
are inhabitants of Earth, and as I said, we

190
00:10:48.750 --> 00:10:51.150
could have meaning with regard to just a few

191
00:10:51.150 --> 00:10:54.469
people in our immediate surroundings, or we might have

192
00:10:54.469 --> 00:10:57.390
a broader meaning, uh, that could be felt, let's

193
00:10:57.390 --> 00:11:00.070
say, around the earth. Now, there can also be

194
00:11:00.070 --> 00:11:01.869
degrees of meaning of this kind. So somebody might

195
00:11:01.869 --> 00:11:04.630
have a very small positive global impact, or they

196
00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:07.270
may have a very large positive, uh, global impact.

197
00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:10.200
But I don't think that there can be any

198
00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:13.880
meaning from a broader perspective. Now, not in principle.

199
00:11:13.940 --> 00:11:18.520
I mean, let's imagine that the universe was In

200
00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:21.380
was inhabited by other species on other, on other

201
00:11:21.380 --> 00:11:25.039
planets, and things that people did here had significance

202
00:11:25.039 --> 00:11:27.679
in those other planets. Well, then there might be

203
00:11:27.900 --> 00:11:32.570
some small quantity of, of positive cosmic meaning. Uh,

204
00:11:32.900 --> 00:11:35.340
BUT on the understanding that there are no sentient

205
00:11:35.340 --> 00:11:37.380
beings elsewhere, or at least that we're having no

206
00:11:37.380 --> 00:11:40.820
impact on those sentient beings elsewhere, I think that

207
00:11:40.820 --> 00:11:43.900
cosmic meaning is absent. Another possible way of having

208
00:11:43.900 --> 00:11:46.520
cosmic meaning is if there were a God. WHO

209
00:11:46.520 --> 00:11:49.960
would have a kind of cosmic perspective and if

210
00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:54.219
things that you do did matter to God, then

211
00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:55.669
that might be a way you could get it.

212
00:11:55.719 --> 00:11:57.380
I just don't think that there is a God

213
00:11:57.719 --> 00:12:00.539
who Uh, would give that kind of meaning to

214
00:12:00.539 --> 00:12:01.239
our lives.

215
00:12:02.280 --> 00:12:05.419
Yes, I'm also an atheist, but I was wondering,

216
00:12:05.679 --> 00:12:10.479
since you mentioned that possibility, which I don't even

217
00:12:10.479 --> 00:12:13.320
think is a possibility, but anyway, let's consider it

218
00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:16.039
just for the sake of the argument. If there

219
00:12:16.039 --> 00:12:21.760
was such a God and created us as human

220
00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:25.840
beings as a special kind of creation in the

221
00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:30.719
universe, do you think that could imbue. Our lives

222
00:12:30.719 --> 00:12:32.599
with cosmic meaning.

223
00:12:33.390 --> 00:12:35.609
Yes, it might be a small dose of it,

224
00:12:36.140 --> 00:12:38.460
depending on just how important this purpose was for

225
00:12:38.460 --> 00:12:40.700
which God had created human beings and also more

226
00:12:40.700 --> 00:12:43.820
particularly individual human beings because he might have a

227
00:12:43.820 --> 00:12:46.580
grand purpose for the species as a whole, and

228
00:12:46.580 --> 00:12:49.679
yet any individual human being is just a cog

229
00:12:49.869 --> 00:12:53.140
in that whole purpose, or it might be that

230
00:12:53.140 --> 00:12:56.719
God has some very important purpose for each individual.

231
00:12:56.940 --> 00:12:59.390
Now, it's very, very hard for me to fathom

232
00:12:59.700 --> 00:13:03.219
what that might be. Uh, BUT, uh, if there

233
00:13:03.219 --> 00:13:05.460
were such a thing, then I think that would

234
00:13:05.460 --> 00:13:07.500
be a form of cosmic meaning. There'd then be

235
00:13:07.500 --> 00:13:10.919
a further question about how significant it was, how

236
00:13:11.260 --> 00:13:12.820
big it is, how big the meaning is.

237
00:13:14.140 --> 00:13:18.109
And and of course, there's uh we can establish

238
00:13:18.109 --> 00:13:23.039
a link here with religion more broadly. What do

239
00:13:23.039 --> 00:13:26.640
you think about what we could call, of course

240
00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:30.719
as atheists, perhaps other people would call it or

241
00:13:30.719 --> 00:13:33.960
use other terms, but what do you think about

242
00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:39.679
coping mechanisms that people resort to like the ones

