00:13:39.679 --> 00:13:46.719
provided by religion which in their own subjective understanding

244
00:13:46.719 --> 00:13:48.859
provide their lives with meaning.

245
00:13:49.799 --> 00:13:51.150
So, I do think this is part of the

246
00:13:51.150 --> 00:13:55.219
explanation of the enduring feature of religion is that

247
00:13:55.219 --> 00:13:58.119
it does provide a coping mechanism, and one of

248
00:13:58.119 --> 00:14:00.760
the coping mechanisms that it can provide is the

249
00:14:00.760 --> 00:14:05.039
sense that your life has a purpose beyond the

